task.summary: Initial commit: an idea for Lab 5 - students would refactor code to introduce type hierarchy and replace switch statements with dynamic dispatch.
Worked on UI - customer list and invoice list models added. Artificial data added in response to button clicks.
Re-worked UI to use JTable instead of JList

Loaded initial data into table.
Cleared out fields that are not used from model.
Added customer cell renderer so that customer fields are coloured based on whether or not customer is in good standing.
Refactored UI to introduce CustomerPanel and InvoicePanel classes with simpler communication model between customer table and invoice table.

Removed CustomerListener interface and increased coupling between CustomerPanel and InvoicePanel.
Can make it a lab or lecture-lab exercise to apply Observer pattern and add a new observer to listen for changes to customer data.
Regrouped constants in ServiceRecord to make them easier to separate by ServiceType when refactoring
Simplified colouring of cells in renderers
Fixed bug in colouring of cell renderers
Modified InvoicePanel so that an invoice is always selected (if there any to select).
